			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Other changes:
<br />

<br />
In addition, Absor stopped by our forums and noted that a few things were left out of the patch message that we'd want to know about (thanks, Absor!) 
<br />
- Made Fire Beetle Eyes stackable 
<br />
- Made the Lightning Core stackable. 
<br />
- Changed the name of the Gnomish Vanishing Device to Half Capacity Gnomish Vanishing Device. 
<br />
- Created the Full Capacity Gnomish Vanishing Device. 
<br />
- Created a Collapsed Distillery, there's a new Collapsible Container Study that has the details 
<br />
- Added Putrescent Blood drops to NPCs outside of the intestine event in Plane of Disease. 
<br />
- Ordin Wheasly, Tylida Eraldi and Phranz Tyudin in Abysmal now sell Dried Vanilla Beans and Rock Salt. 
<br />
- Changed the Kelp Salts ingredient in the basic Ice Cream recipes to a new item called Rock Salt which can be purchased from the baking vendors in Abysmal. 
<br />
- The Ice Cream Churn is now a "tradeskill container" and you can learn recipes for that container. 
<br />
- Increased the drop rate on the following Planes of Power Temper and Armor materials to bring them more in line with the others: Metallic Substance, Gaseous Condensate, Fog Fragment, Air Arachnid Silk, Chips of Granite and Storm Volaas Hair. 
<br />
- Changed the recipes for the magnetic armor in Omens. They now require patch plates (from 1 to 4) for every item. This brings the component requirements in line with the other armor types. 
<br />
- Changed the recipe for Aldo’s Bitter Ale – Bottle to use a bottle and a cork instead of a cask. 
<br />
- The recipe for researching Servant of Bones will now work as described in the in-game text.
<br />
We mentioned that some recipes had become learnable. Here are some of them: 
<br />
- Bristlebane Party Platters 
<br />
- Ceremonial Solstice Robe 
<br />
- Dreams of Drusella 
<br />
- Rage of Incapacitation 
<br />
- Wasted Flesh 
<br />
- Enchanted Velium Bits 
<br />
- Crystalline Silk Swatch 
<br />
- Advanced Propulsion Unit 
<br />
- Base Prototype 
<br />
- Perpetual Air Pump 
<br />
- Perpetual Steam Pump<br />_________________<br /><img src="http://members.aol.com/twiggiebrell/jaradissig.jpg" border="0" />
<br />
